INSERT INTO `` (`DeptCode`,`CourseNo`,`CourseName`,`No_credits`,`Descrip`,`notes`) VALUES ('ALIN','2101','Intermediate Modern Standard Arabic',3,'Emphasizes the acquisition of vocabulary and increases the command of grammatical and syntactical structures. Further develops reading, writing, listening, and speaking skills. Two semester sequence.','Any two consecutive can be taken simultaneously. Prerequisites are not listed for every course. However, entry into all intermediate and advanced presupposes that the student is of intermediate or advanced standing. The instructor’s permission may also be required. Standing will be determined by written and/or oral placement tests for incoming students and sometimes for continuing students.');
INSERT INTO `` (`DeptCode`,`CourseNo`,`CourseName`,`No_credits`,`Descrip`,`notes`) VALUES ('ALIN','2111','Intermediate Writing',2,'Develops students’ ability to meet short practical writing needs. Trains students to summarize informative and narrative passages, gradually introducing more complex structures..','Prerequisites are not listed for every course. However, entry into all intermediate and advanced presupposes that the student is of intermediate or advanced standing. The instructor’s permission may also be required. Standing will be determined by written and/or oral placement tests for incoming students and sometimes for continuing students.');
INSERT INTO `` (`DeptCode`,`CourseNo`,`CourseName`,`No_credits`,`Descrip`,`notes`) VALUES ('ALIN','2121','Intermediate Reading and Writing',3,'Develops reading and writing by integrating the two skills in one course and introducing a wide variety of modern Arabic texts to be used for reading and a basis for writing assignments. The course develops the students’ reading comprehension, vocabulary acquisition and acquaints them with the style of the Arabic essay. It prepares the student for the more sophisticated course in advanced reading and writing.','Prerequisites are not listed for every course. However, entry into all intermediate and advanced presupposes that the student is of intermediate or advanced standing. The instructor’s permission may also be required. Standing will be determined by written and/or oral placement tests for incoming students and sometimes for continuing students.');
INSERT INTO `` (`DeptCode`,`CourseNo`,`CourseName`,`No_credits`,`Descrip`,`notes`) VALUES ('ALIN','2131','Intermediate Printed Media',2,'Exposes students to a wider range of topics selected from the Arabic press. Emphasizes vocabulary and idiom acquisition, and begins to develop students’ ability to read for speed.','Prerequisites are not listed for every course. However, entry into all intermediate and advanced presupposes that the student is of intermediate or advanced standing. The instructor’s permission may also be required. Standing will be determined by written and/or oral placement tests for incoming students and sometimes for continuing students.');
INSERT INTO `` (`DeptCode`,`CourseNo`,`CourseName`,`No_credits`,`Descrip`,`notes`) VALUES ('ALIN','2133','Intermediate Aural Media',2,'Further develops students’ listening skills while expanding their vocabulary, especially in the areas of politics and economics. Increases their ability to comprehend details.','Prerequisites are not listed for every course. However, entry into all intermediate and advanced presupposes that the student is of intermediate or advanced standing. The instructor’s permission may also be required. Standing will be determined by written and/or oral placement tests for incoming students and sometimes for continuing students.');
